Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}神虎 閃耀 之刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香凜大人 列席人士一如預想都已離開會場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有報告稱ZERO出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO？第三隊 報告突入情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三隊 是否已成功支援星刻？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說我們的計策被ZERO利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 你無意返還聖上麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻 你以為自己能讓天子獲得自由？你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連KMF都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到斬月的第一件工作會是幫忙搶婚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂 拿下修奈澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想拐走殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是籐堂先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈澤爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘的交給軍隊 我們也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 這邊跟計劃的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 進入第三階段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟紅蓮一樣的系統？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來能行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠這斬月 就算對手是朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這招的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開得了槍嗎 這個位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把朱禁城…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木朱雀 死在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂鏡志朗 還沒到時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰之太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了浮空裝置又如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還裝有這樣的武器麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂 暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Lancelot的浮空裝置破壞掉就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經無法追擊我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天子陛下 很快就要到朱禁城外了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調龍騎兵部隊過來 把聖上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後的事情由我們處理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想從我方雷達監視網的間隙中逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 他們怎可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本佬漂流到這裡才不到10天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂將軍 先從千葉的曉開始進行補給吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬月和紅蓮等回到斑鳩後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們照這個去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下來往左
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎 天子陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是外面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會用如此粗暴的方式 實現天子陛下的夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你也一樣記得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 太纏人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊涼快去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下來往右
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 直走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識路的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有過點因緣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可以將我合眾國日本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當作是更加強大的合眾國聯盟的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合眾國中華 為此我們需要您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經和南部省 印度軍區達成協議
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古和緬甸隨後也會行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合眾國聯盟 將成為對抗布里塔尼亞的軸心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我記得我國是聯邦制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制度是有壽命的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大宦官為了保身 企圖把您出賣給布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可饒恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 太複雜的事我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天子陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎星刻 是與您互定終身的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有… 只是有過約定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說是婚約？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是想去外面的約定 六年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼早就定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是您的真命天子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 都交給神樂耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天子看來不是適合講道理的對象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應付不來？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是難以分析罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說ZERO 我的官職還沒決定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都一直打拼到現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就給我財務大臣或金融長官的職位…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉城當宴會太政大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說別開這種玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我們不是好朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事等逃出這裡再說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 橋不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是禁軍第四守備隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對像在笙中停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群愚蠢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟預想的一樣 設好陷阱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 全軍 準備攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右發現敵軍 被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊 快攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 聖上在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來試試新型機的武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追擊部隊被擊潰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點在笙中溪谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我 會在那裡設伏兵拖住陸軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小沛和大部隊匯合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻 想免你的罪也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你把聖上奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個借你用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧德修斯殿下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平靜下來了 正在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 等Lancelot換好部件就去救天子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進一步的軍事行動要等待中華聯邦的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我能理解 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進展比預想要順利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都多虧了星刻他們的計策嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常優秀 那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼知道他們在策劃政變的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也打算干同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括電子干擾與伏兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有一條計劃路線被人搶先 試圖解除我們的機關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從在場的叛軍那裡知道的麼 用自白劑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做GEASS的自白劑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓬萊島的情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印度方面的援軍已經抵達了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有回去後跟他們匯合 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天子陛下方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方的KMF部隊正被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 全軍停止前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算遭遇敵軍也應該在一小時以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人識破我們的行動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KMF？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和我們一樣安裝著滑翔翼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KMF 神虎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也才只是40%的功率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死太監 竟有這等東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是可翔型 但終究只有一機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包圍後殲滅！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小看這神虎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 無道之人休要吠叫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 此路不通
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我就是問為什麼會停在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這裡是完全隔音的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 把聖上還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還能饒你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮可翔式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅月卡蓮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要有這神虎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬月能出擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部件剛剛才撤下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 還沒補給呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架紅蓮和圓桌騎士都能打個勢均力敵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我可是黑色騎士團的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她見識一下 神虎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展示你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們小組製造的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克夏塔的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和紅蓮同時期開發的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但過於追求高性能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導致無人能夠駕馭的孤高Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是神虎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃這招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天愕霸王荷電粒子重炮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和輻射波動炮彈同等的破壞力？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機體怎會落到敵人手中？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明印度也沒那麼團結啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩訶羅闍那臭老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有弱點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和其他系列的理念就不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了沒有輻射機構外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的弱點也就是找不到機師而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在不是有人正在駕駛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已決
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下你逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 直接給你轟進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實非得已 只好殺了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺得到就殺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說先補給啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛艙區塊被纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣無法逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夾擊 弄斷神虎的鋼線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管並不想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是為了我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是聖上 要將聖上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得及反應麼 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後方出現中華聯邦軍 是大部隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續對空射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩護星刻大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香凜嗎 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別 慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡 卡蓮…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被中華聯邦軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被俘虜？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮 無線還能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我失態了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別提這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放棄 我一定會救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到沒 別輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓斑鳩轉向 立刻！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我建議撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 必須救回卡蓮才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅月卡蓮不過是一介士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要見死不救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 這是選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇中華聯邦這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:13:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一個人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本無法相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該保存兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備與印度軍匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 請下決定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅月隊長有您剛才的通話就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多的表示將被視為偏袒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會導致組織崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同情與判斷難道不該區別看待嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現遠大理想 有時也需要犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 圓桌騎士的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作個了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍掉頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 這也是為了組織…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印度軍也有可能背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓千葉和朝比奈布下鶴翼陣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給星刻上堂課
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他知道戰略和戰術的區別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還在待機命令中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 朱雀君知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯特雷姆卿的手機圖像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 能看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來參加歡迎會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱私都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他幹什麼呢 都已經有夏莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿修弗德的聯絡 目前正在確認
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會在擔心呢 魯路修他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是 魯路修？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團 全軍戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地形上高低差不大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不指望地形優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上敵軍只是臨時拼湊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮系統只可能集中在ZERO身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是敵方KMF的性能在我之上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 中華聯邦的選擇必然是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以神虎為先鋒的中央…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神虎就由這斬月來對付
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三龍騎兵部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射程我方佔優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊炮擊邊突進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓制住敵方指揮官了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉隊 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算星刻無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂同樣無法脫身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來就看士兵的經驗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓制敵艦正面天任區劃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍左右兩翼無視便是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有紅月果然略遜一籌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方本陣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍在正面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 條件滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右翼千葉軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左翼朝比奈軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟用Σ模式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防備後方射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對敵方本陣布下彈幕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊先頭部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引誘神虎用盡能源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓制星刻我們就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進 在此停下我們會全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把卡蓮還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引入白兵戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉全軍之力來對付我嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太依賴神虎的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不過是有勇無謀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是為了試探ZERO行動的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一配置的真正意義是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻 運河決堤就是你的策略嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 水量已經減少過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為這招不值一提？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是那個灌溉開拓地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腐敗造成的豆腐渣工程
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其結果ZERO也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前的突擊是為了引誘敵軍主力進行移動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻大人單騎突進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓ZERO在此地停步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他都看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會發動決戰 乃至採用這個佈陣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我們帶來勝利的 正是我國的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負還未分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是奇跡的籐堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 敵軍主力已經停在了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部隊開始進軍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍Knightmare部隊稍後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中炮火攻擊敵艦動力部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對物理障壁也不是無窮無盡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利屬於我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟把我逼到被各個擊破？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等醜態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 我建議過撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護動力部 後退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回蓬萊島也沒用吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇 那個地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 偵查和測量基本都完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承認 星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該先擊殺你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我相當的智略
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及朱雀水準的勇武
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天竟然將兩樣都賜給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 沒有賜給他的只有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撐住 還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦首 擴散強子重炮啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豐饒女神系統控制 同步正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準調整 可以發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 瞄準敵軍兩翼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是ZERO 竟然還有招數
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各龍騎兵部隊散開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站著不動會成為靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂負責部隊救援與重編隊指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑鳩迂迴牽制敵軍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往第4預定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中華聯邦的新聞 哪個台都沒播啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘存全Knightmare 收容完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要據守在天帝八十八陵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭祀歷代天子的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確敵人也難以攻擊這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人只能從正面來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時用艦首強子重炮攻擊即可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說不能連射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就等印度軍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒援軍的守城戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣的話倒還有交涉的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到大宦官會用那一手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了叫你不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾對我等掀起反旗之人不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是說這個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 不是應該奪回聖上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到這一步就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有強大的援軍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒算到還有圓桌騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中華聯邦竟要求助於他國 求助於布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那艘艦是Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底明不明白 大宦官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方可是奪取了半個EU的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二皇子修奈澤爾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大宦官不僅針對我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還打算在此抹殺星刻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪哈爾特 快去準備機關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都湊齊了 這不是最棒的舞台嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要贏給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是在這絕望的形勢下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後續報導發來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面播報中華聯邦的形勢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著政變進行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO出現 虜獲了天子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,700)}天子的安否目前…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事啊 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 跟朱雀君他們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們那邊的新聞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在電視和廣播裡一色兒的ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 會長還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:21:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國臣民之敵ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎會在海洋對面的中華聯邦迎來末路
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠狠的 這形勢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今再對天子施加Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做我的僕從也沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻也遲早會被大宦官肅清
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我們正被逼得走投無路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有籐堂他們在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早朱雀也會出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利的概率無限的小
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰術上的戰鬥我要徹底顛覆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會在此結束


